                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Ahora me pregunto si un par de Decretos Legislativos valen todo el odio y dolor que generar\x{e1}n estas muertes.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 32,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 449
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Se podr\x{e1} ahora hablar de una soluci\x{f3}n pacifica y concertada con tantas muertes a cuestas (sobre todo cuando ya la Ministra del Interior ha declarado que Pizango y compa\x{f1}\x{ed}a deben ser detenidos y puestos a disposici\x{f3}n de las autoridades \x{2013} RPP 16:30) Lamentablemente comenzar\x{e1} la caser\x{ed}a por encontrar a los responsables \x{201c}pol\x{ed}ticos\x{201d} e \x{201c}ideol\x{f3}gicos\x{201d} de esta masacre; qu\x{e9} actitud que tomar\x{e1} el parlamento respecto a los decretos a\x{fa}n es incierto (seguramente estar\x{e1}n pensando m\x{e1}s en la censura ministerial que en otra cosa); lo \x{fa}nico claro es que el tema de fondo que en alg\x{fa}n momento pudo discutirse \x{201c}el modelo de desarrollo amaz\x{f3}nico\x{201d} solo sabe Dios cuando volver\x{e1} al debate p\x{fa}blico.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 33,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 450
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'Now I wonder if a few legislative decrees are worth all the hatred and pain that have caused these deaths.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 34,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 451
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "We could now talk about a peaceful and agreed upon resolution at the cost of so many deaths (especially when the Minister of Interior has stated that (indigenous protest leader) Pizango and others should be arrested and brought to the authorities - 16:30 RPP) Unfortunately, the hunt will begin to find those \x{201c}political\x{201d} and \x{201c}ideological\x{201d} individuals responsible for the massacre; what position will the parliament take on the decrees is still unclear (surely they are thinking more about ministerial censure, than anything else), the only thing clear is that main issue that could have been discussed \x{201c}the model for Amazon development\x{201d} only God knows when it can return to public debate.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 35,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 452
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Peruvian ex-pat in Spain, Jomra unequivocally criticizes President Garc\x{ed}a [es] , who said [es] that the protesters were wrong and that they cannot tell 28 million of Peruvians that they are not welcome in that region and by doing so they are stepping into irrationality and \x{201c}primitive retreat.\x{201d}",
                                   'sentence_number' => 36,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 453
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Jomra writes about Garc\x{ed}a:",
                                   'sentence_number' => 37,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 454
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "No solo es mentiroso, sino que es intolerante e ignorante de la propia Constituci\x{f3}n y los tratados que Per\x{fa} ha firmado. ...",
                                   'sentence_number' => 38,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 455
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Pero lo importante es el fondo: El presidente asume que puede aplastar lo que la Constituci\x{f3}n y el Convenio OIT n\x{ba} 169 Sobre Pueblos Ind\x{ed}genas y Tribales en Pa\x{ed}ses Independientes (de 1989, entr\x{f3} en vigor en el 91 y Per\x{fa} lo ratific\x{f3} en el 94), en la primera se establece una entidad jur\x{ed}dica especial para las Comunidades nativas y campesinas que el ejecutivo debe respetar y en el segundo se obliga a que toda decisi\x{f3}n que afecte a las comunidades sea previamente consultada.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 39,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 456
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'El DL 1090 no lo ha sido.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 40,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 457
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Garc\x{ed}a cada vez que puede acusa a la dirigencia de las comunidades de manipular a los pobres ignorantes, a la vez que pone que todo esto est\x{e1} orquestado por otros pa\x{ed}ses, no se atreve a acusar a Venezuela pero indica que a quien conviene es a Chile (supongo que en el vecino del sur se mueren de risa al o\x{ed}r los desprop\x{f3}sitos de Garc\x{ed}a).",
                                   'sentence_number' => 41,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 458
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'Not only is he a liar, but he is intolerant and ignorant of the Constitution and treaties which Peru has signed. ...',
                                   'sentence_number' => 42,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 459
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'But the most important thing is: The president assumes that he can discard what is outlined by the Constitution and ILO Agreement No. 169 concerning Indigenous and Tribal Peoples in Independent Countries (1989, entered into effect in 1991 and ratified by Peru in 1994).',
                                   'sentence_number' => 43,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 460
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'The first establishes a special legal entity for the indigenous and peasant communities and farmers, and that the executive branch must respect this entity.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 44,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 461
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'The second requires that any decision affecting the community must be in consultation.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 45,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 462
                                 },
                                 {
