                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'She also criticizes the media for their role during this crisis:',
                                   'sentence_number' => 50,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 467
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Tambi\x{e9}n lo es que la indiferencia e incluso la justificaci\x{f3}n de muchos comentaristas y bloggers, que haya gente que es capaz de aceptar estas muertes como necesarias para mantener el orden y el desarrollo significa que a\x{fa}n estamos muy lejos de ser un pa\x{ed}s que pueda caminar hacia adelante.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 51,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 468
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Es vegonzoso como los medios de comunicaci\x{f3}n como Peru21, El Comercio, RPP, desinforman a la poblaci\x{f3}n y se dedican a poner a la opini\x{f3}n p\x{fa}blica en contra de las protestas sociales, ya sea minimizando las muertes que los nativos han sufrido, escondiendo informaci\x{f3}n o exagerando y dandole un spin t\x{e9}trico a las noticias.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 52,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 469
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'es',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => "Esto tambi\x{e9}n pasa con alguna prensa internacional, Sim\x{f3}n Romero del NYT hace una nota sobre la protesta, mezcla el conflicto con Sendero Luminoso, (y) presenta a los nativos como anti-desarrollo.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 53,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 470
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'It is also the indifference and even the justification from many commentators and bloggers, who are people that are able to accept these deaths as necessary to maintain order and development, that means that we are still far from being a country that can move forward.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 54,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => 471
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-04-16 08:32:44.761678-05',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'It is shameful that media such as Peru21, El Comercio, RPP, misinform the public and devote themselves to sway public opinion against the social protests, either by minimizing the deaths that the natives have suffered, hiding information or by exaggerating and giving a grim spin on the news.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 55,
                                   'stories_id' => 8,
