                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 13:13:48',
                                   'sentence' => 'This also happens with some international press, Simon Romero of the New York Times writes an article about the protest, but mixes the conflict with the Shining Path, (and) presents the natives as anti-development.',
